                        <interp inst="t18450915-name-505" type="given" value="ELIZA"></interp>ELIZA CAIGER</persName>
                  </hi>. I am the wife of Edward Caiger, and am a washer-woman. I employed the prisoner—on the 12th of Aug. I left home be<lb></lb>tween two and three o'clock—I came back about half-past four, and found the prisoner was gone—she did not return—I missed my shawl and flan<lb></lb>nel petticoat—I have not found my shawl—this is my petticoat—it is marked.</p>
